episodes.title: New lead? Theory links Gardner art heist to Jeffrey Epstein files
episodes.description:
Thirty-six years after the Gardner Art Heist, no one knows where the stolen art is right now, but a recent social media post suggesting the Epstein files might contain a new lead is getting a lot of attention.

Find more at Boston25News.com: https://www.boston25news.com/news/local/new-theory-linking-epstein-files-gardner-art-heist-debunked/ZSFF3ENJTBF2ZCJCUOT26TTODY/
